Media query: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media

[CSS Box Alignment](https://www.w3.org/TR/css-align-3)

![Box aligment properties](/assets/img/css/box_alignment_properties.png)

* `first-child`
* `first-of-type`

[Answer](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/24657555/what-is-the-difference-between-first-child-and-first-of-type)

```css
<div class="parent">
  <h1>Child</h1>   <!-- h1:first-child, h1:first-of-type -->
  <div>Child</div> <!-- div:nth-child(2), div:first-of-type -->
  <div>Child</div>
  <div>Child</div>
</div>
```

